Name: Resultarias
About the game: Resultarias is a surrealist adventure game narrated by dream exploration. You play as 'Utsuki', a girl that for some reason doesn't want to leave her room and will only explore the world through her dreams. The game features various worlds, characters, items that can be collected on the dream world and used for various purposes but mainly helping the exploration and advance through the narrative.
